## A Closing Word on the Card

The eight fields never change. The Dish, Done Means, Prep by Hand and Watch For are yours before AI arrives. Bring in AI is bounded. Who Signs is named. Plate and Taste is the proof. Serve is the release and the lesson. Run them in order and the discipline holds itself up.

The kitchen teaches discipline. This starter set teaches the first six dishes. The rest is practice.

**Final Liability rests with the Human.**
